{"tid":1318534,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Marvel隊長》非裔女星傳將接棒演占士邦","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T18:30:40.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":332,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"a974333bd2af3c759f1b0ad5f5da1a54606a4776","tid":1318534,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"新一集占士邦（James Bond）電影《Bond 25》現正趕拍中，今日有報道傳出最後一次飾演占士邦的男星丹尼爾格力（Daniel Craig）會在片中向軍情六處（MI6）辭職，並將占士邦這個007代號交給由英籍非裔女星Lashana Lynch飾演的新角色Nomi。正式結束多年來的特務生涯！亦意昧着往後的007電影將由Lashana擔正。 <br />\n<br />\n007將由非裔女星接替的消息傳出後惹來大批fans不滿，有fans認為非裔男星艾迪斯艾巴（Idris Elba）更適合接替之餘，亦有fans認為呢個決定必定會毀滅占士邦系列。更有fans留言指占士邦的已故原作著伊恩費林明（Ian Fleming）都會嬲到在墳前彈起！ <br />\n<br />\n現年31歲的Lashana擁有牙買加血統，於英國倫敦Hammersmith出世，初入行時以拍劇為主，直至今年她憑漫威（Marvel）的超級英雄電影《Marvel 隊長》（Captain Marvel）空軍機師Maria Rambeau一角成名。新一集邦片將於來年4月8日上映。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190715/photo/bkn-20190715100911385-0715_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190715104526\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190715%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190715100911385-0715_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190715104526&h=b3dd81a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4beba29825a82fe7b7260f43e012a1ad839bf225","tid":1318534,"uid":182930,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"到時真係搵鬼睇囉"},{"pid":"d8e358f62d899b5c94e71da7ac35cc760c10981f","tid":1318534,"uid":66839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"唔係short 到咁啊"},{"pid":"38d0abfaa669308488574ee6a2a127220356e91b","tid":1318534,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":70,"score":-67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"我又幾期待力架妹做JAMES BOND<br />\n<br />\n幾新懶"},{"pid":"ff107f041d33d1f2b1eb25e22ea60e497b526cff","tid":1318534,"uid":39470,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"Captain Politically Correct"},{"pid":"d25b71275