on bourne，票房一樣唔靚。<br />\nEthan Hunt就搞唔到，一嚟已經變成Tom Cruise代名詞，二嚟個故事仲未完，Tom Cruise仲有心有力可以拍落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKingsman就算數啦，最搶鏡都係Colin firth。第二集一減少戲份，成套戲已經唔收得。<br />\n難得007作為特工電影可以橫跨幾個世代，而家想打爛招牌，大家可以睇吓一套冇英式紳士型男、冇靚女嘅007票房可以有幾災難。"},{"pid":"01e8cdd7569726e83a29c843da57b133f893d612","tid":1318534,"uid":187368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"跟住又講佢係les<br />\n然後係到溝白人女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f8a270638d2dd439622745f6ce3372bc84ef2d","tid":1318534,"uid":63853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"黑人都唔夠 要女黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d7e8d363ce7ffb14a317bafc84fb3d1cdeeacd","tid":1318534,"uid":130118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:52:11.000Z","msg":"Ghost Buster<br />\nMen In Black <br />\n衰左兩鑊仲未識死"},{"pid":"808503715eb46dc6feef0c846eb5fe7dd4c499c6","tid":1318534,"uid":39287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:25:00.000Z","msg":"到時全部黑人都會睇 之後拎埋奧斯卡 今次仲唔fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0234949d1e1a515304c2ce98352bab33736011a0","tid":1318534,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"睇下之前本身男演員改用女演員既重拍作品<br />\nGhostbuster, Ocean seven, 結果搞死左自己個系列<br />\n佢007要用用女演員既話, 佢真係隨時斷送007呢個系列品牌"},{"pid":"23c9d96afe5f0c97c6f8822bcb407c896e8b2147","tid":1318534,"uid":39320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:44:10.000Z","msg":"正呀 幾時拍返套GODMOTHER <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fa268cdca4ffa008933